OL,15,Fprice cap rocketing to more than
OL,16,F#4,000 a year for the typical
OL,17,Fhousehold, although households
OL,18,Freceived #400 towards their bills,
OL,19,Fwhich were limited by the government's
OL,20,Fenergy price guarantee to an average
OL,21,F#2,500.
